" provided.  When a v:count is provided, move by logical lines.
nnoremap <expr> j v:count > 0 ? 'j' : 'gj'
xnoremap <expr> j v:count > 0 ? 'j' : 'gj'
nnoremap <expr> k v:count > 0 ? 'k' : 'gk'
xnoremap <expr> k v:count > 0 ? 'k' : 'gk'

